    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing to achieve a 100+ hp-per-liter output. Power is channeled through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a speed-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its signature balance, featuring aluminum control arms and a subframe that remains structurally sound. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh, ensuring the valvetrain operates with peak harmonic precision. A driver-focused example that maintains excellent mechanical compression and tactile steering feedback.",
