      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid, dependable shape and has been well-loved over the years. It runs great and is just waiting for its next adventure! If you're looking for a quality vehicle that won't break the bank, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
