      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus. This unit delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its composure with a factory-tuned multi-link rear suspension and staggered alloy wheels. Critically, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal (RMS) is dry. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative, offering the precise turn-in signature unique to the rear-engine layout. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-rash consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchro mesh is smooth and the braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers with ample rotor life remaining.",
